    <item>
      <title>Episode 1: Understanding Lightning Network Fundamentals</title>
      <description>In this foundational episode, we break down the core concepts of the Lightning Network. We explore payment channels, how they enable instant Bitcoin transactions, and why Lightning is crucial for Bitcoin's scalability. We also discuss the value-for-value model and how podcasters can monetize content directly through Lightning payments embedded in RSS feeds.</description>
