    <!-- Episode 2: Lightning Addresses and Value-for-Value -->
    <item>
      <title>Episode 2: Lightning Addresses and the Future of Podcast Monetization</title>
      <description>This episode explores Lightning addresses - the email-like identifiers that make Bitcoin payments as simple as sending an email. We discuss how podcasters are using Lightning addresses and value blocks in their RSS feeds to create sustainable revenue streams. Learn about the technical implementation and real-world examples of successful value-for-value podcasting.</description>
