    <!-- Episode 3: Keysend Payments and Node Routing -->
    <item>
      <title>Episode 3: Keysend Payments and Advanced Lightning Routing</title>
      <description>In this technical deep-dive, we explore keysend payments - a Lightning Network feature that allows payments to be sent directly to Lightning nodes without requiring an invoice. We discuss how keysend works, its advantages for podcast monetization, and the challenges of Lightning routing. Plus, we'll show you how to set up your own Lightning node for receiving keysend payments.</description>
